                <h3 class="card-title">Thaddeus Kosciuszko National Memorial</h3>
                <br/>
                <p>Visit the house where wounded Polish freedom fighter Thaddeus Kosciuszko lived and hear how this brilliant military engineer designed successful fortifications during the American Revolution. See the room where he received notable visitors such as Chief Little Turtle and Thomas Jefferson.</p>
                <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
